Type: Package
Package: REDesignR
Title: REDesignR: Restriction Enzyme Digests Simulation and Visualization
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Christine", "Cheng", , "christineentse.cheng@mail.utoronto.ca",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The main purpose of the tool is to help scientists determine
    the best restriction enzyme(s) to use for their sequence digestion
    experiment.  The tool will be an R package with a Shiny interface that
    simulates, optimizes and visualizes restriction enzyme digestion
    experiments.The tool automates optimal enzyme choice, provides
    intuitive visualization/interactive interfaces, and simulates
    multi-enzyme co-digestion experiments.
